  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Add, edit, delete, and search books.</li>
    <li>Issue and return operations with validation and availability management.</li>
    <li>Overdue detection with automatic fine calculation.</li>
    <li>Dashboard statistics and report generation.</li>
    <li>CSV import/export and local data persistence.</li>
    <li>SMS reminders for due and overdue books.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Conclusion</h2>
  <p>
    The project demonstrates practical software engineering with object oriented principles and layered design.
    It is suitable for academic submission and can be extended with database integration and web-based modules.
  </p>
